1
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:30,430
Rinkham,

2
00:00:30,984 --> 00:00:32,980
where have you been loitering this time?

3
00:00:41,970 --> 00:00:43,218
Have you been mischievous again?

4
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:47,132
I only came to watch the soldiers today.

5
00:00:49,130 --> 00:00:50,270
This is my friend.

6
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:58,492
Have you come to enlist as a soldier?

7
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,664
Yes, sir.

8
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:12,116
Record his name.

9
00:01:12,369 --> 00:01:12,886
Yes, sir.

10
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:29,144
Are these all the real deal?

11
00:01:31,610 --> 00:01:32,880
My Lady, please don't play with that.

12
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:33,809
It is dangerous!

13
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:34,923
Wow, this is pretty heavy.

14
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,120
Oh my!

15
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,923
That was a close!

16
00:01:41,390 --> 00:01:43,249
Are you always this mischievous?

17
00:01:45,778 --> 00:01:47,770
I used to sneak out my dad's sword to play with when I was a child.

18
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,867
But dad would never teach me how to use it.

19
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:52,941
Come on,

20
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,670
try sparring with me for a bit.

21
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:58,473
Let's see if you are fit to be a soldier.

22
00:01:59,030 --> 00:02:00,024
Put it down.

23
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,292
It's dangerous.

24
00:02:02,410 --> 00:02:03,341
If that's the case,

25
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:05,920
then come make me put it down.

26
00:02:06,701 --> 00:02:07,673
Oh! Please be careful.

27
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:24,529
Do you know how dangerous that was?

28
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:29,821
Sometimes, danger excites me.

29
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:35,249
Can you teach me the way of the sword?

30
00:02:39,323 --> 00:02:40,055
Fall in!

31
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:46,350
I have to go line up now.

32
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,467
Go for it! Kaew,

33
00:02:49,450 --> 00:02:50,701
my brave soldier.

34
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:03,944
Isn't his face a bit too clean and pretty?

35
00:03:05,070 --> 00:03:08,141
He’s so small, can he even be a soldier?

36
00:03:11,850 --> 00:03:14,695
Hey... we’re talking to you. Why aren't you answering?

37
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,403
You’re talking nonsense.

38
00:03:18,570 --> 00:03:19,920
Why should I answer you?

39
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,381
We’re speaking to you nicely.

40
00:03:22,418 --> 00:03:23,501
Are you trying to be a smartass with us?

41
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,815
And why are you bothering me in the first place?

42
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:30,756
So you can learn that you don't belong here!

43
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:45,956
Then, Am I fit to be a soldier now?

44
00:03:46,730 --> 00:03:48,024
You dare to slash my throat?

45
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:53,206
I would never use my dad's sword to spill the blood of an unworthy enemy.

46
00:04:53,650 --> 00:04:54,849
Have you been here long?

47
00:04:55,690 --> 00:04:56,529
Why do you ask?

48
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,073
No reason.

49
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:01,772
What are you doing here anyway?

50
00:05:03,033 --> 00:05:05,030
I just wanted to come and watch what just happened.

51
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:07,335
You’re much better than I thought.

52
00:05:35,784 --> 00:05:39,421
It would have been a shame if you didn't make the cut.

53
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,590
Let’s go,

54
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,261
they’re about to announce the results in front of the house.

55
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:53,907
Thong-ek.

56
00:05:53,926 --> 00:05:54,486
Yes, sir.

57
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:55,187
Suea.

58
00:05:55,410 --> 00:05:55,956
Yes, sir.

59
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,126
Chai.

60
00:05:57,156 --> 00:05:57,716
Yes, sir.

61
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:58,676
Man.

62
00:05:58,695 --> 00:05:59,120
Yes, sir.

63
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:02,338
And the last one... Klao.

64
00:06:02,375 --> 00:06:02,892
Yes, sir.

65
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:08,676
I told you, you shouldn't have wasted your time applying.

66
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:11,421
Someone like you... could never be a soldier.

67
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,760
If you don't want a repeat of what just happened,

68
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,667
keep your mouth shut.

69
00:06:21,050 --> 00:06:21,926
Stop.

70
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,587
You are Kaew, right?

71
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,593
Yes, sir.

72
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,498
You possess great skill.

73
00:06:31,126 --> 00:06:33,120
You know how to restrain yourself

74
00:06:33,163 --> 00:06:34,750
and keep your emotions in check.

75
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:38,418
I need someone like you to be Rinkham's bodyguard.

76
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,236
Dad!

77
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:46,363
But I don't want someone tailing me everywhere.

78
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:49,156
Your safety is paramount, my daughter.

79
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:53,680
Well, are you interested?

80
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,513
Even though I enjoy having fun with you,

81
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:08,670
I don’t want someone following me wherever I go.

82
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:13,064
But I have already given my word to Luang Witsanu.

83
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:18,584
Therefore, it is my duty to stay by your side and protect you.

84
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:23,421
I am not an easy person to take care of, you know.

85
00:07:25,910 --> 00:07:28,166
And I am not someone who gives up easily either.

86
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:34,683
Well then, let's just see about that.

87
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,593
The situation lately has been unstable.

88
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:03,680
I request approval for additional weapons and troops.

89
00:08:04,227 --> 00:08:05,680
It is not yet necessary.

90
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,932
But the news of the other side's movements...

91
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:09,181
I know!

92
00:08:10,890 --> 00:08:14,030
Do not let paranoia drive you to overreact.

93
00:08:15,130 --> 00:08:18,412
I have made my decision, and you must follow it.

94
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:19,926
Yes sir.

95
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:33,895
This person is such a nuisance.

96
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:35,889
He refuses everything I ask for.

97
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:39,403
It seems I will have to find a way to eliminate him...

98
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,516
I need to find...

99
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,729
a weakness to take him down.

100
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:06,510
Are you Kaew, the new bodyguard for Lady Rinkham?

101
00:09:07,140 --> 00:09:07,895
Yes, I am.

102
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:11,507
By the way... which way is the Young Miss's room?

103
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:13,698
Over that way.

104
00:09:14,978 --> 00:09:15,833
Thank you.

105
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,664
Lady Rinkham is quite a handful.

106
00:09:22,701 --> 00:09:25,132
He'll probably be running scared before the day is out.

107
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,861
Lady Rinkham?

108
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:34,141
She has gone out.

109
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:36,720
Gone where?

110
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:39,126
I do not know,

111
00:09:39,156 --> 00:09:41,120
She has been out since before dawn.

112
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,012
Then why did no one follow her?

113
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:47,329
Well… She strictly forbade anyone from following her..
